              },
              "free_text": [
                " CaCO3 and TiO2 targets with",
                "different enrichment in 43Ca, 44Ca and 46Ti",
                "isotopes were used. The targets were produced by",
                "sedimentation on aluminum backings. The target",
                "thickness was estimated to be in the order of 10",
                "microns. The surface of the targets was covered by 10",
                "micron thick Al foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC",
                "SITA",
                "EDEG",
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiations at",
                "several energies were performed. The initial beam",
                "energy was 18.4 MeV, which was varied by aluminum",
                "absorbers. Irradiations typically lasted 3-5 mins,",
                "whereas the beam current was in the order of tens of",
                "nA. The measurement method was verified by",
                "remeasuring the cross section of natTi(P,X) 48V and",
                "natCu(P,X) 63Zn reactions with the same setup, and",
                "comparing it to recommended values by IAEA."
              ]
            }
          ],
